%B0%E3%80%80%E9%85%92%E6%A8%93%E8%AA%A4%E5%B0%87%E8%9B%8B%E7%B3%95%E7%95%B6%E5%A3%BD%E5%8C%85%E6%B8%85%E8%92%B8%E3%80%80%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhongkongmooncake.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F03%2F10%2F%25E6%25AF%2594%25E8%2592%25B8%25E6%259C%2588%25E9%25A4%2585%25E6%259B%25B4%25E5%25B4%25A9%25E6%25BD%25B0%25E3%2580%2580%25E9%2585%2592%25E6%25A8%2593%25E8%25AA%25A4%25E5%25B0%2587%25E8%259B%258B%25E7%25B3%2595%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%25A3%25BD%25E5%258C%2585%25E6%25B8%2585%25E8%2592%25B8%25E3%2580%2580%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BE%258C%2Famp%2F&d=eRHmMhW6fCYgFX7Mu85bUhnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=483e25d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hongkongmooncake.wordpress.com/2018/03/10/%E6%AF%94%E8%92%B8%E6%9C%88%E9%A4%85%E6%9B%B4%E5%B4%A9%E6%BD%B0%E3%80%80%E9%85%92%E6%A8%93%E8%AA%A4%E5%B0%87%E8%9B%8B%E7%B3%95%E7%95%B6%E5%A3%BD%E5%8C%85%E6%B8%85%E8%92%B8%E3%80%80%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C/amp/</a><br />\n<br />\n沒有最崩潰，只有更崩潰。日前有網民在facebook群組「Tai Po 大埔」轉貼一名僱主的手機截圖指，家中菲傭自創「清蒸」冰皮月餅，令僱主哭笑不得，但暗黑料理又豈止這一款。有網民憶起2011年風靡一時的OpenRice「蒸壽包」潮文，DJ森美更曾在電台節目公開全篇朗讀一遍。雖然當年潮文被瘋傳，但最終的結局未必人人知道，原來事主「案發」後9個月親自回應，指酒樓「一句道歉都冇」。<br />\n<br />\n2011年網民在食評網OpenRice留言指，屯門一間海鮮酒家的侍應將他親手製作的「壽桃蛋糕」清蒸，他寫道：「昨晚到此酒家食晚飯慶祝我婆婆生日，本人親手用左大半日時間，整左個壽桃蛋糕俾婆婆慶生。一去到酒樓，我就將蛋糕交左俾一個侍應阿姐，叫佢幫我雪住個蛋糕。」<br />\n<br />\n嘔心瀝血自製蛋糕竟被摧毀，該事主稱氣得無法形容：「只可以當場痛哭。」他更嬲爆反問：「如果我個蛋糕係魚形，咁佢地係咪會拎去煎黎食？」事後森美曾在電台節目聲演這篇潮文，網民大讚他將事主無奈又憤慨的心情表露無遺。<br />\n<br />\n吃完主菜後，事主拜託侍應拿出蛋糕，對方竟表示找不到及從來沒幫他保存蛋糕，經過一輪了解，事主終於得悉令人崩潰的真相，「發生左一件俾食客誤食更慘痛既情況出現」，他接着寫道：「佢地竟然話我知，將我個蛋糕拎左去蒸，佢仲話我個蛋糕唔係蛋糕，係壽包！」"},{"pid":"7357f8b80df821fb4a4d22fab652b4c6f3798183","tid":2433100,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T02:27:43.000Z","msg":"紅蘿蔔蛋糕?"},{"pid":"129ad82a07ed8b33796b7b1c3eca9fe0cc2fbf59","tid":2433100,"uid":314129,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"d68588de6971e194977f84f12f756b508140d428","tid":2433100,"uid":326151,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T20:07:22.000Z","msg":"就咁戚風蛋糕已經好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T02:31:17.000Z","msg":"戚風蛋糕唔係要加cream先好食咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1896db8559f2cb767613d1e957c9171918f0a8d","tid":2433100,"uid":314129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c6efaa3626499de20d18200f68eef2ba869e561","tid":2433100,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"40cef8bf0d151bd3a52455110c26a76bebda71fe","tid":2433100,"uid":314129,"like":0,"dislike":22,"score":-22,"quote":{"pid":"31e3a9362e219f5c0d334775c54586499cabcadd","tid":2433100,"uid":304355,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T18:00:08.000Z","msg":"鮮果蛋糕（少cream"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T18:19:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zxACGf3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzxACGf3.jpg&h=312046f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好似呢個咁？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T22:16:43.000Z","msg":"呢個得，但係頂要多士多啤梨🍓，老人家喜事唔鍾意白色為主，白色對於老一輩黎講唔好意頭。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T02:33:38.000Z","msg":"我加色素轉紅色忌廉咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84658cb8684d97a7a4321bc755c93fabcb3e00a4","tid":2433100,"uid":289701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T03:27:57.000Z","msg":"豆腐蛋糕?"},{"pid":"eba30f9478338bf3942d8fddd1d3b7614b310614","tid":2433100,"uid":393757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T07:42:30.000Z","msg":"野菜蛋糕？"},{"pid":"4a19295a4d0a042e34bc86a93fc9a9dbf78e8911","tid":2433100,"uid":314129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T07:51:38.000Z","msg":"如果整呢個好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vEaZY6v.jpg\" data-thumb